{"parse":{"title":"Raw Nightfin Snapper","pageid":35884,"wikitext":{"*":"<onlyinclude>{{{{{tpl|tooltip}}}\n|mode={{{mode|}}}\n|arg={{{arg|}}}\n|sell={{cost|c=10}}\n|icon=INV_Misc_Fish_23\n|quality=Common\n|itemid=13759\n|ilvl=45\n|name=Raw Nightfin Snapper\n|level=35\n|effect=Use: Restores 810 health over 27 sec.  Must remain seated while eating.}}</onlyinclude>\n\n== Source ==\n{{Accuracy-section|Locations need checking.}}\n'''Raw Nightfin Snapper'''  are found in inland water and can only be caught between the times of 6 PM and 6 AM (except as noted below).\n\nNightfin Snapper can be caught in [[Azshara]], [[Badlands]], [[Deadwind Pass]], [[Felwood]], [[Feralas]], [[Moonglade]], the [[Plaguelands]], [[Silithus]], [[The Hinterlands]], [[Un'Goro Crater]], [[Winterspring]], inside the [[Temple of Atal'Hakkar]] in the [[Swamp of Sorrows]], and inside [[Zul'Farrak]] and [[Zul'Gurub]].\n\n==Raw Nightfin Snapper as an ingredient==\nThis item is used to make: \n* {{loot|Common|Nightfin Soup}}\n\n== Notes ==\n*The [[Tainted Forest]] in the southern [[Blasted Lands]] is a very good place to catch these fish.\n*The best time to catch Nightfin Snappers is between 12 am and 6 am (except as noted below).\n*The recommended locations are [[Deadwind Pass]], [[Eastern Plaguelands]], [[Silithus]], [[Winterspring]] and [[Zul'Farrak]].\n*A couple of good places to secretly fish for Nightfin Snappers are at the pool of [[Gahz'rilla]] in [[Zul'Farrak]], and inside the [[Temple of Atal'Hakkar]] (outside the instance though) in the [[Swamp of Sorrows]].  In both places you can also get [[Raw Sunscale Salmon]] fish.\n* You actually can catch Nightfin Snappers during the daytime, by fishing inside the [[Temple of Atal'Hakkar]].  On September 6, 2010, Nightfin Snapper was caught at the [[Frostfire Hot Springs]] in [[Winterspring]] at 11 am server time.  It is unknown if this phenomena is unique to this location or an indication that they may be rarely caught at any time.\n*On March 7, 2011 a Nightfin Snapper was caught in Moonglade at 9 AM server time. Several were caught, so the time table theory is becoming quite shaky.\n\n==External links==\n<!-- Read http://www.wowwiki.com/WoWWiki:External_links before posting your links here.\nLinks that do not conform to the rules will be DELETED.\nRepeat violations may result in a BAN.\nHave a nice day. :) -->\n{{elinks-item|13759}}\n{{Elink|link=http://www.elsanglin.com/fish/raw_nightfin_snapper.html |site=El's Extreme Anglin' |icon=elsanglin}}\n[[Category:World of Warcraft common fished items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft food items]]\n[[Category:World of Warcraft cooking ingredient items]]"}}}